Auto generate thankyou cards for Christmas / Birthday / Bar Mitzvah gifts.

Can pull a colour scheme from colourlovers.com API at http://www.colourlovers.com/api/palette/#{id}

Installation:
- Requires Ruby to be installed. Written with Ruby 2.1.3, although 1.9.3+ is probably fine.
- The only dependency is Prawn; install it using 'bundle install' if using Bundler, else 'gem install prawn'.

Usage:
- Edit config.yml as neccessary. Add a block under 'cards' for each card to create.
- Then 'ruby main.rb'

Available fonts:
- Courier
- Helvetica
- Times-Roman
- Symbol
- ZapfDingbats
- Courier-Bold
- Courier-Oblique
- Courier-BoldOblique
- Times-Bold
- Times-Italic
- Times-BoldItalic
- Helvetica-Bold
- Helvetica-Oblique
- Helvetica-BoldOblique

Available border styles:
- "circles"
- "squares"
